strings: <voice_0x010017C2><se_low>jungmi: I know you think we're hiding something. None <hero>,
<voice_0x010017C3><se_low>jungmi: I know you but you like me, am I waiting for this moment?
<voice_0x010017C4><se_low>jungmi: I don't want to do anything to hinder Lord Dragovia's recovery of health.
<voice_0x010017C5><se_low>jungmi: We promise all of this will be revealed to you when you arrive at the LifeDrag cave.
<se_low>jungmi: It's getting late, so let's go back to our room and rest.
<voice_0x010017C6><se_low>jungmi: I still haven't slept How are you? sleep well?
<voice_0x010017C7><se_low>jungmi: I am glad that I trusted you.
<voice_0x010017C8><se_low>jungmi: So, in extreme cases, it's not surprising. But I believe in their power.
<voice_0x010017CA><se_low>jungmi: The path is a veritable labyrinth. Entrance is through the living room door downstairs.
